# Day 862

It is hard to accept that many times our biggest enemy can be ourselves. The good news is that our biggest supporter is the same person. It all comes down to how you engage with yourself.

"Whether you think you can or think you can't, you're right" - Henry Ford

Do the damn thing. Stop scrolling feeds, listening to the naysayers, worrying about what if. DO. THE. DAMN. THING.
